<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/470927-about-a-year-ago-i-stopped-reading-this">About a year ago I stopped reading this book and I&#39;ve been stuck on page 403 ever since. I do want to finish it, but am afraid to start reading again because I feel I probably forgot a lot of the terminology and the story. I also don&#39;t want to start over. Can anyone recommend me a good summary I might read?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_470927'><a id="like_count_community_question_470927" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/470927?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F2845024-anathem">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
