<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5350955080523914441">Neal Stephenson is the author of <i>Reamde, Anathem,</i> and the three-volume historical epic the Baroque Cycle (<i>Quicksilver, The Confusion,</i> and <i>The System of the World</i>), as well as <i>Cryptonomicon, The Diamond Age, Snow Crash,</i> and <i>Zodiac.</i> He lives in Seattle, Washington.</span>

